<h2><p><%= t('.greeting', recipient: @resource.email, default: "Welcome to Dhisha, #{@resource.email}") %></p></h2>

<h3>Before you can access your account, we request you to confirm your email id by using the link below.</h3>


<h3><p><%= link_to t('.action', default: 'Confirm my account'),
         confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token, locale: I18n.locale) %></p></h3>

<p>Please note that by confirming your email id, you agree to grant us permission to contact you occasionally via email. We shall not spam you.</p>

<p>Once you confirm your email id, please update your profile details by clicking on your name in our website and following the Update profile link. </p>


<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>Dhisha human development trust.</p>
